== 發行 ==
=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度73%，基於網站收集的223篇評論，平均分為6.23/10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_secret_life_of_pets |title=''The Secret Life of Pets'' (2016) |website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2016-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161112195217/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_secret_life_of_pets |archive-date=2016-11-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]獲得61分<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-secret-life-of-pets |title=The Secret Life of Pets reviews |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2016-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716010529/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-secret-life-of-pets |archive-date=2016-07-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，口碑良好。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「A-」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |accessdate=2016-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150217211441/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |archive-date=2015-02-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國和加拿大，預測於首映週末能獲得約7000萬美元的票房，甚至有些專家預測高達1億美元<ref name="DEADproj">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/07/star-trek-beyond-box-office-projection-ghostbusters-secret-life-of-pets-1201782223/|title=‘Star Trek Beyond’ Could Hit $60M Opening, According To Some Early Projections|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2016-07-01|accessdate=2016-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702143748/https://deadline.com/2016/07/star-trek-beyond-box-office-projection-ghostbusters-secret-life-of-pets-1201782223/|archive-date=2016-07-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/07/the-secret-life-of-pets-mike-and-dave-need-wedding-dates-box-office-preview-1201782755/|title=‘The Secret Life Of Pets’ To Give ‘Dory’ The Hook; ‘Mike And Dave’ Targets Millennials – Box Office Preview|author=Anita Busch|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2016-07-05|accessdate=2016-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160706153433/http://deadline.com/2016/07/the-secret-life-of-pets-mike-and-dave-need-wedding-dates-box-office-preview-1201782755/|archive-date=2016-07-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/box-office-secret-life-pets-dory-mike-and-dave-1201808792/|title=‘Secret Life of Pets’ to Fetch Strong Debut at U.S. Box Office|author=Dave McNarry|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2016-07-05|accessdate=2016-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160707013934/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/box-office-secret-life-pets-dory-mike-and-dave-1201808792/|archive-date=2016-07-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-secret-life-908745|title=Box-Office Preview: 'Secret Life of Pets' to Bite Off $70M-Plus Debut|author=Pamela McClintock|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2016-07-06|accessdate=2016-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160707151225/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-secret-life-908745|archive-date=2016-07-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

美國首映週末開出了1.04億美元的票房佳績位居當週第一，比預期的還高<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/07/10/weekend-box-office-secret-life-pets|title=Box office: Secret Life of Pets roars past $100 million|author=Joey Nolf1|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2016-07-10|accessdate=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711122258/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/07/10/weekend-box-office-secret-life-pets|archive-date=2016-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這打破了《[[腦筋急轉彎_(電影)|腦筋急轉彎]]》（9040萬美元）的最高首映週末原創與非續集動畫片的紀錄。

